{"tid":1922270,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"買Parton相買到欠左幾萬蚊卡數，就黎要食二手飯。。。","createTime":"2020-03-12T12:50:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-14T12:47:20.000Z","uid":58335,"like":15,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"c0edf2b6feeea70f981d5ca80274f7c0cb526407","tid":1922270,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T12:50:56.000Z","msg":"今日有個悲慘既故事要同大家分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有留意開我以前既故事既都知<br />\n我識親既女都唔正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n已經唔夠係現實識港女<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知比我早排係連登發現左一個叫Parton既網<br />\n個到有大量靚女相買<br />\n咁我係對港女死心，但又想睇靚女既情況下<br />\n咁唯有去個到買相<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n初初買左Deer Chan D相<br />\n跟住愈買愈多<br />\n買埋FuFu、MK妹Ruby、中大Email等等。。。<br />\n<br />\n前幾日見到張信用卡原來已經欠緊幾萬蚊卡數。。。<br />\n我做保安師<br />\n一個月先得9000蚊<br />\n扣扣埋埋使費<br />\n已經冇錢剩。。。<br />\n幾萬蚊卡數真係唔知點還。。。<br />\n琴晚仲同媽咪借左1000蚊<br />\n呃佢拎黎買口罩<br />\n但最後我都係再去左Parton買相<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我覺得自己好似買到上左癮咁。。。<br />\n今個月得返98蚊係身上<br />\n都唔知點頂到月尾<br />\n唔通真係要去快餐冶到食二手飯??<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3da1455e94fcf2e6ba8a16dd40e2fc75874e9b7b","tid":1922270,"uid":82829,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T12:52:46.000Z","msg":"快趣收返個奴叫佢比錢你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話係命令"},{"pid":"8ee430d4e6275bca724b097b5c3d3e6c1731d212","tid":1922270,"uid":209391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T12:53:29.000Z","msg":"圖定伯母？"},{"pid":"ddf66b37ab6b4406e47fab5c05d297831b9dc894","tid":1922270,"uid":58335,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"8ee430d4e6275bca724b097b5c3d3e6c1731d212","tid":1922270,"uid":209391,"like":0,"disli